      "id": "2045156267690213649",
      "text": "Introducing Claude Design by Anthropic Labs: make prototypes, slides, and one-pagers by talking to Claude.\n\nPowered by Claude Opus 4.7, our most capable vision model. Available in research preview on the Pro, Max, Team, and Enterprise plans, rolling out throughout the day. https://t.co/2BgBGtgYGX",
